{"tid":1279720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勾結齊國人系列//1//","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:47:16.000Z","uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eea633202f176c508157643c59748868ed2d04c6","tid":1279720,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:45:02.000Z","msg":"凡先處戰地而待敵者佚，後處戰地而趨戰者勞。<br />\n故善戰者，致人而不致于人。<br />\n能使敵自至者，利之也；<br />\n能使敵不得至者，害之也。<br />\n故敵佚能勞之，飽能飢之，安能動之。"},{"pid":"f6d3a05cb0b598e7ea5516235f63f216e1c20bab","tid":1279720,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}